Packages 
Package Description
org.shanerx.tradeshop.enumys
This package contains all the enum types the plugin's internal API makes use of.
org.shanerx.tradeshop.framework
This package contains the TradeShop Addon Framework (TSAF), though most things apart from the utility enum ShopChange.
org.shanerx.tradeshop.framework.events
This package contains all classes belonging to the TradeShop Addon Framework (TSAF), a framework which allows external plugins to listen in on Trade-events, so that they may enhance Trading experience through the addition of external features.
org.shanerx.tradeshop.objects
This class contains all the classes of the core of the plugin.
org.shanerx.tradeshop.utils
The classes in this package contain several useful tools for Bukkit/Spigot plugin development, which can be reused beyond TSAF purposes.
